Disclaimer: 
  Don't count on these apis yes, since they might change =x !
  I will publish an official api on the website when ready.


Current producton api routes:
==============================

  Get testimonials
  --
    GET: http://api.pluspanda.com/testimonials.[:format]?apikey=abcd
    
      Required query string params
        valid apikey  
        
      Optional query string params
        sort = "newest"
        tag  =  string
        page = integer
        
      Available formats [:format] : 
        json, js (jsonp callbacks)    
    
      Live Example call:
       http://api.pluspanda.com/testimonials.json?apikey=nbE6zpH&sort=newest&page=1
       http://api.pluspanda.com/testimonials.js?apikey=nbE6zpH&sort=newest&page=2


  Load widget javascript environment
  --
    GET: http://api.pluspanda.com/testimonials/widget.js?apikey=abcd

      Required query string params
        valid apikey
      
      Also Required:
        To run this script on your page you need to also include a div tag:
          
          <div id="plusPandaYes"></div>
          
        Which pluspanda will render your testimonials in.  
          
      Live Example Call:
        http://api.pluspanda.com/testimonials/widget.js?apikey=nbE6zpH
      
      
  Add a new testimonial (web page)
  -- 
    GET: http://api.pluspanda.com/testimonials/new?apikey=577ed4ada1f60e44

      Required query string params
        valid apikey

      Live example Call:
        http://api.pluspanda.com/testimonials/new?apikey=nbE6zpH

  Add a new testimonial
  --
    POST: http://api.pluspanda.com/testimonials?apikey=577ed4ada1f60e44

      Required query string params
        valid apikey
      
      Required POST params:
        All testimonial fields are optional.
      
      Optional POST params: 
        testimonial[name]  
        testimonial[rating]  
        testimonial[company]  
        testimonial[c_position]  
        testimonial[location]  
        testimonial[body]  
        testimonial[url]  
        testimonial[position]
      
        TODO:  
          testimonial[avatar]
          testimonial[tag_id]  
                

  Edit an existing testimonial (web page)
  --  
    GET: http://api.plusanda.com/testimonials/70/edit?apikey=577ed4ada1f60e44
      renders a full webpage.
      
    Live Example Call:
      http://api.pluspanda.com/testimonials/2/edit?apikey=nbE6zpH
      
  Edit an existing testimonial.
  --    
    POST: http://api.plusanda.com/testimonials/70/edit?apikey=577ed4ada1f60e44
      Returns the full webpage with edit status.
      Todo: verify return a json status string.
      
      Required GET data (via query string)
        valid testimonial id
        valid apikey
      
      Required POST data:
        All testimonial fields are optional.
    
    
 
    
old api:
============

  full public testimonial add form:
   http://pluspanda.com/testimonials/add/cI7eHaw






javascipt widget run through:
-----------------------------
assert panda.init called? 
in panda.init  
  assert jquery exists?
    on false
      append google cdn
      assert jquery exists via polling
      polling expecting jquery true
    on true 
      assert setup called?
      in setup
        assert append css link
        assert store updated panda container
        assert delegate events on container
        assert getTstmls called?
        in getTstmls
          assert jsonp ajax call is made 
          assert jsonp callback triggers:
            panda.display
            in panda.display
              assert content string is created.
              asset content string is added to the DOM
          
            panda.update
            in panda.update
              assert total count is updated
              assert pagination is updated
